    <text id="F4004T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>McClure expresses reluctance to leave home until he knows of the safety of the
                    border near the Potomac and asks for news.</p>
            </div1>

        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>Private
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1862-05-25">May 25</date>
                        <name type="place">Chambersburg</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute><abbr expan="Dear">Dr</abbr> Sir</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>Our people are nervously anxious about the safety of the border, because of the
                    retreat of Banks.</p>

                <p>I cannot <unclear>of come</unclear> conjecture what the real state of the case
                    is, but I must not leave home until the safety of the Potomac line is assured. I
                    have written the <abbr expan="Governor">Gov</abbr> returning the <unclear/> 7000
                    judgement, &amp; telling him to have Fuller send me <unclear>
                        <hi rend="underline">Fuller</hi>
                    </unclear> check to paynote here and to have you pay in
                    <unclear>Binkeriger</unclear> &amp; Farm &amp; <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>. He
                    assured me that he would do so, &amp; F. will keep an eye to it.</p>

                <p>Write me how matters go, and telegraph me the war news <hi rend="underline"
                        >honestly</hi> for our people are wild on the subject.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>
                        <unclear>Yours</unclear>
                    </salute>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="underline">AKMcClure</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
